Job Description
If you are experienced British Property Agent, with a proven success record, we will be glad to see you in our team. We offer: Competitive package with basic salary, high commission, paid leave, paid annual ticket and medical insurance. Prime office location in downtown Dubai. Strong marketing support Vast property owner’s database And many more Send your updated CV and recent photo to the email address mentioned, and start your career with us !!
